		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />One could move the frames before the frames I removed closer to the frames after, so long as the spacing didn't end up even again.<br /><br />Or to remove no frames, just retime it so that each frame falling frame gets less exposure time which is something games have the luxury of doing. Even if removing no frames, keep the ponytail thing in mind.

		

		</td>
