		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It depends on what it is you are trying to do. I take longer doing pixel art on nes format than I do for snes on top of that I work even faster spriting high res (guilty gear) or even hd (persona arena) nes ever got damn pixel counts. One missed place pixel can screw up the whole thing. Some people just don't care but to me it bothers me and I will sit there for hours to get it right even if I have to redraw the crap over and over.<br /><br />I hate franken spriting and I hate spriting over something and calling it my own unless it was my own sprite to begin with. So yeah.

		

